    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Orchestrate a multi-step process with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive in real time\n\n**Pattern:** Workflow Automation · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Scheduled\n\n## What it does\nOrchestrate a multi-step process with HTTP / REST API and Google Drive in real time. It runs automatically on a schedule.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual triggers is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nWeekly Schedule → Normalize Job Payload → Route by Work Type → Process 'sync' → Google Sheets → Merge Routed Work → Save Execution Metadata → Guard Non-Empty type → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to workflow automation without manual effort\n- Anyone automating triggers in productivity\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Improves response time\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.",
        "width": 480,
        "height": 900
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -830,
        80
      ],
      "id": "b914a5b6-25a6-a6b5-c6c9-28e79aab7a31",
      "name": "📘 Workflow Overview"
    },
